commit.message:
Updated support status for several plugins

Updated pipeline support for plugins: HttpRequest, PerformancePublisher, HockeyappRecorder, ghprb and test-results-analyzer. Checked support via Jira, PRs, changelogs. Confirmed HttpRequest by checking syntax snippet.

